title: Rock 'n' Roll Years BBC TV Series 1975 To 1979
description:
BBC TV Series: The Rock 'n' Roll Years

Documentary series which revisits the years from when rock 'n' roll began, connecting the events with the music via newsreels, headlines, movies, broadcasts, and rock performance footage.
